Package edu.monash.fit2099.interfaces

Interface ActionInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Action, AttackAction, CraftWeaponAction, DoNothingAction, DropDefreezeItemAction, DropItemAction, EatingHealAction, FertilizeAction, HarvestingAction, KickAction, MoveActorAction, PickFreezeItemAction, PickUpItemAction, PlayerEatingAction, SowCropAction, SpitBehaviour, WindowSmashAction, ZombieAttackAction
public interface ActionInterface
This interface provides the ability to add methods to Action, without modifying code in the engine, or downcasting references in the game.
